", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75280177_1012617213990979_1732549949916101256_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FpiZTk26Z3QQ7kNvgGD7hIF&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBo9xahusWZT1vfxG6DJGhPIwbBcNaMc1dJe45yNhHgKw&oe=677FA338"}, {"file_name": "image5.png", "id": "27882995044633476", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974864_27882995047966809_2560160188894003364_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wynLPt7FWe8Q7kNvgHd8l-b&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCE2OXQlR_6L4ggYqsNK81p_jYza6GLgrh5vg0EmpkNqA&oe=677FA179"}, {"file_name": "image2.png", "id": "410575135384874", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974821_410575138718207_8230945586108737660_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=BrzFEwPoToUQ7kNvgHbUZCH&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDVydToc8A9r_tAEBn9g_6QUbfsiOS6FG1qoYFsZuC2Ng&oe=677FBF58"}, {"file_name": "image1.png", "id": "1057387732496751", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75540501_1057387735830084_2190979014283040881_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Tc_o41ao3RoQ7kNvgGwa5-m&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBtpyXJTOb1tnw0a38GIRpUpnC4tRoem8zsTMRXONHo2Q&oe=677FCA73"}, {"file_name": "image4.png", "id": "1151089155995496", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974848_1151089159328829_2039739925044486928_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=l0EBtbAtzJ8Q7kNvgFiUGiQ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBHGkXQrcwZrM-UC31o0j7jk_8Xn1JwdAzFSfMUkkrI7g&oe=677F9C2F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Keyart_2560x1440.png", "id": "1984373528679847", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974591_1984373532013180_122028893976097645_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qEg1T2l_6OAQ7kNvgFM3CNJ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBo072g5zuNTlT7uqvIn_hosVqZLvWwrpsQAld6-aTz4w&oe=677FAF3B"}, "display_name": "My Monsters Demo", "keywords": ["Monsters", "Third", "Free", "Puzzle", "My"], "long_description": "My Monsters is an action-adventure VR game featuring *100% hand-painted art*, creating a visually stunning world full of fantasy and surrealism.\n\nAt the heart of the game lies a deep narrative exploring humanity's greatest inner struggles\u2014anxiety, fear, and loneliness. As the player, you are transported to Onirium, a *dream-like realm* where you encounter Moti, a frightened little monster with no memory.\n\nIn My Monsters, you\u2019re never alone. *Team up with your inner monster*, Moti, to face a variety of enemies, solve intricate puzzles, and overcome challenges in a shared journey. This partnership mechanic fosters a powerful connection with Moti, requiring empathy and courage to navigate obstacles and reveal fragments of a *meaningful dreamlike tale*. Every stage introduces new aspects of this bond, allowing players to experience moments of self-discovery and emotional depth.\n\nKey Features in the Demo:\n\n\n\u2694\ufe0f  Combat Enemies: Engage in dynamic combat with enemies.\n\n\ud83e\udde9  Solve Puzzles: Challenge your critical thinking and problem-solving skills.\n\n\ud83c\udf19  A Dream-like Tale: Uncover a touching, emotional narrative that delves into themes of self-reflection and growth. \n\n\ud83c\udfa8  100% Hand-Painted Art: Every visual element in the game is carefully crafted by hand, creating a beautiful, one-of-a-kind experience. \n\n\ud83e\udd1d  Team Up with Your Inner Monster: Build a meaningful relationship with Moti, using teamwork, empathy, and courage to overcome every challenge.\n\n*THE GAME IS IN DEVELOPMENT, AND ITS CONTENT MAY CHANGE.*", "short_description": "My Monsters is a VR action-adventure game featuring stunning 100% hand-painted art. In this demo, you\u2019ll explore Onirium, a dream-like world filled with emotional depth, as you face humanity's greatest inner monsters like anxiety and fear. Meet Moti, a scared little monster with no memory, and team up to battle enemies, solve puzzles, and overcome challenges. Unravel fragments of a dreamlike narrative as you journey together. The game is currently in development, and its content may change."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://mymonsters.ludact.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Ludact", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://mymonsters.ludact.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "528142316460358"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8686086238127538"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036697_535483152192630_2729698551779994031_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2OZUcm5tO04Q7kNvgH7v8nE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAga-hLAWgwzWk2tuUCEb8-A00dB7qkoEMHqacRh_w0Uw&oe=677FBF83"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "My Monsters Demo", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "GAMES", "id": "2743326035925534"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "Adventure", "id": "2691890164460465"}, {"topic_name": "Action", "id": "45978